name: Public Display of Value
description:
An experimental, conceptual NFT.

This NFT will display the top ten prices that have been paid for itself.

51 editions will be created.

10 will be released at 0 Tez
24 hours later, unsold editions will be burnt and 10 will be released at 1 Tez
24 hours later, unsold editions will be burnt and 10 will be released at 10 Tez
24 hours later, unsold editions will be burnt and 10 will be released at 100 Tez
24 hours later, unsold editions will be burnt and 10 will be released at 1000 Tez

1 will remain unreleased
